  https://github.com/ggml-org/llama.cpp
  Pinned release: b9957
  Copyright (c) 2023-2026 The ggml authors
  Licensed under the MIT License.
  License text: https://github.com/ggml-org/llama.cpp/blob/b9957/LICENSE

whisper.cpp / whisper-cli runtime
  https://github.com/ggml-org/whisper.cpp
  Pinned release: v1.9.1
  Copyright (c) 2023-2026 The ggml authors
  Licensed under the MIT License.
  License text: https://github.com/ggml-org/whisper.cpp/blob/v1.9.1/LICENSE

OpenAI Whisper multilingual model weights and whisper.cpp GGML quantizations
  https://github.com/openai/whisper
  https://huggingface.co/ggerganov/whisper.cpp/tree/5359861c739e955e79d9a303bcbc70fb988958b1
  Optional local speech-recognition models: Whisper Small Q5_1 and
  Whisper Large v3 Turbo Q5_0.
  The OpenAI Whisper source code and model weights are licensed under the
